Note:
(m) mandatory
(o) optional

Difficulty:

Function:
    add_buyer: 
            Input: name (m)
            Do: add the person name into file '.persons'


    log_deal: 
            Input: name (m), money-paid (m), money-cost (m), item (o)
            //Do: sanity check paid and cost [cost should < paid]
                Mark current date time into system

    check_buyer:
            Input: name (m)
            Do: Dump person buy information
                format-table money-paid, money-cost, profit, time, item
                final line total money-paid, total money-cost, total profit from the person

